subgraph Page_18 [Page 18]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_2_308f5f1e["6.2 Safety Committees"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_2_1_5d9c027f["6.2.1 The contractor shall contribute to<br/>safety committees and other liaison<br/>activities"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_2_2_c6dbace3["6.2.2 The contractor shall provide<br/>visibility of the information set to the<br/>safety committee"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_2_3_7bac4d3a["6.2.3 The contractor shall support the<br/>safety committee in recommending,<br/>endorsing or providing guidance"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_2_4_35f53ea6["6.2.4 The contractor shall support the<br/>safety committee in any additional<br/>roles/tasks"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_2_5_26565fe4["6.2.5 Where there is an appropriate UK<br/>MOD safety committee, the contractor<br/>shall participate"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_2_6_f07a791d["6.2.6 Where there is no appropriate<br/>safety committee, the contractor shall<br/>work with the UK MOD"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_2_7_a762fa40["6.2.7 Where appropriate the safety<br/>committee may delegate work to<br/>subsidiary committees"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_2_8_063ed569["6.2.8 Where the contract involves<br/>support, the contractor shall ensure the<br/>safety committee approves changes"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_2_9_8a048aff["6.2.9 The contractor shall record all<br/>their support given to the safety<br/>committee"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_3_85fcccb1["6.3 Competencies"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_3_1_14819bdc["6.3.1 The contractor shall ensure that<br/>all safety-relevant tasks are carried<br/>out by competent individuals"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_3_2_91b47c8c["6.3.2 The contractor shall record the<br/>evidence of competence"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_6_3_3_f4eec01c["6.3.3 The contractor shall undertake<br/>competence management"]
