subgraph Page_32 [Page 32]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_30db1da7["12.2 Monitoring, Reporting and In-<br/>service Data Analysis"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_1_e67bf150["12.2.1 The contractor shall define and<br/>operate a process for collecting,<br/>analysing and documenting safety-<br/>relevant in-service data"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_2_1ac8e8c9["12.2.2 The contractor shall review the<br/>safety case in light of the recorded<br/>data"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_3_52a57635["12.2.3 The contractor shall sentence the<br/>results of analysis of the data"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_4_d501cba1["12.2.4 The contractor shall inform all<br/>relevant stakeholders where they have<br/>identified the need for remedial action"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_5_814c53b5["12.2.5 The contractor shall define and<br/>operate a process for collecting and<br/>analysing incident, accident and near<br/>miss reports"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_6_02536083["12.2.6 The contractor shall analyse all<br/>collected data to identify root causes<br/>which require action"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_7_c73fe503["12.2.7 The contractor shall monitor and<br/>report changes to relevant safety<br/>legislation"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_8_836c1549["12.2.8 The contractor shall liaise with<br/>the UK MOD to establish a Failure<br/>Reporting Analysis and Corrective Action<br/>Systems (FRACAS)"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_9_d8bea48b["12.2.9 Where the contractor supports in-<br/>service PSS which are in use by multiple<br/>stakeholders"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_3_40292566["12.3 Remedial Action"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_3_1_3a350dfb["12.3.1 The contractor shall implement<br/>remedial actions to preserve or improve<br/>safety"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_3_2_6eb5376e["12.3.2 The contractor shall plan<br/>remedial actions taking into account the<br/>need for efficient change management"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_3_3_90aa7e28["12.3.3 The contractor shall plan<br/>remedial actions taking into account the<br/>need to deal with foreseeable changes"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_30db1da7 -->|"contains"| DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_1_e67bf150
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_30db1da7 -->|"contains"| DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_12_2_2_1ac8e8c9
