subgraph Page_34 [Page 34]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_3_552e38aa["13.3 Risk Management"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_3_1_d93ab1d9["13.3.1 The contractor shall support the<br/>UK MOD in managing predicted or emergent<br/>risk to life"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_3_2_4da46e07["13.3.2 The contractor shall cooperate<br/>with the accountable persons for<br/>interfacing or interacting services"]
    DEFENCE_STANDARD_00_056_PART_01_INSA_13_3_3_26183034["13.3.3 Where necessary and with the<br/>accountable person’s agreement, the<br/>contractor shall implement immediate<br/>action"]
